content:
Add the Wrap Up Component to the Voice Call Record Page

To let agents generate and view the call summaries, add the Wrap-Up component to the voice call record page in the console.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Customize Application

Open the Lightning App Builder. Next to the voice call record page, click Edit.
Drag Einstein Field Recommendations component on to the record page.
In the Recommendation Type field, select Wrap-Up.
In the Update Action field, select the update action that you created to store the summaries.
Click Save | Activation, and close the Org Defaults pop-up window.

Create a Quick Action to Store the Generated Voice Call Summaries
Map Outputs to Voice Call Summary Fields
title: Adding Wrap-Up Component to Voice Call Record Page
